displayName: City of Oro's, the Noble House of Skio in the Mountains

parameters:
I am Skio, the virtuous one. If you have any troubles,
please feel free to consult with me.

Welcome, noble Skio. I'm glad you came. Without further ado,
let me tell you about the request.

Noble Skio: 'I want you to give donations to the traveling
monks across the country.'

Sofia the monk: Do you mean to donate to individual monks
instead of the Terios Church?

Noble Skio: Exactly! I want you to deliver it to the
traveling monks who spread teachings while on their journey.

Noble Skio: I may not be wealthy, but I want to support the
monks who have strong beliefs... people like them.
Monk Sophia: Understood. I will gladly accept the donation.

Noble Skio: Since I know the approximate locations through
letters, please deliver the donations on my behalf without
fail.
Kind Skio: 'Please, rely on me instead.'
Welcome back, noble Skio! Please tell us about your journey.

Priestess Sophia: Yes, of course. Shall I give the report
myself, or is it alright for me to do it alone?
Noble Skio: Yes, of course. I don't mind at all.

Priestess Sophia: I handed it over to the three female
priests.

Noble Skio: Yes, there is no mistake. I am relieved to know
that it has indeed been handed over to them.

Noble Skio: I have built wealth with the crystals of this
town, and I want to give back to it in any way I can.

Priestess Sophia: I think it's a wonderful initiative. I'm
sure the goddess Imiserinos will be pleased as well.

Priestess Sophia: Without any discrimination... if there are
no ulterior motives.

Priestess Sophia: The support given only to young and
beautiful women, is the return for their bodies... isn't it?

Noble Skio: Are you planning to accuse the Terios Church!? I
have been providing financial support to the church... The
church is on my side!

Priestess Sophia: Oh my, I have no such intention. I simply
wanted to know the truth.
Priestess Sophia: Oh, right... about the reward.

Priestess Sophia (It would be better to have more travel
funds... There is only one thing I should do to this man)

Noble Skio: I will hand over the reward with some extra
compensation! So please pretend you didn't know about this
matter.

Priestess Sophia: Is this all? Oh my, with just this, it
seems like my mouth might slip.

Noble Skio: Don't get too carried away... I don't want to
harm beautiful women.

Priestess Sophia: Hehe, you've been staring at my chest all
this time, haven't you?

Priestess Sophia: For example, if you were able to have your
way with this chest, the amount of the reward would
naturally change, wouldn't it?
Noble Skio: Y-You... Could it be... Is it really okay!?

Priestess Sophia: If I can receive additional compensation,
then this chest will be yours for a little while... only
yours.
Priestess Sophia: Hehe, what will you do?
Would you like to skip the adult scene?
Noble Skio: Haa... haa... It was amazing.

Priestess Sophia: Thank you very much. I will take my leave
now.

Noble Skio: If you ever need support, please contact me. I
want to help a beautiful and intelligent woman like you.

Noble Skio: I understand, I've lost! You're more like a
merchant than a priest, aren't you?
Priestess Sophia: Hehe, I'll take that as a compliment.

Noble Skio: If you ever need support, please contact me. I
want to help a beautiful and intelligent woman like you.
Priestess Sophia: Yes, I will consider it.

Kind Skio: If you have any troubles, please feel free to
consult with me about anything.
Do you want to skip the adult scene?
It's good to see you again... I'm really happy!

Pure-hearted Skio: Now, bare your chest... and kneel before
me, right in front of my eyes...
